{"tid":775614,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"投訴MK車PD7342","createTime":"2018-08-11T10:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T10:08:09.000Z","uid":80308,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5b51453b19dfe553a0c1ea7afb2bfdddf466ecaa","tid":775614,"uid":80308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"馬路上既TESLUN, BENZ L,定DC9雖然都係唔少仆街<br />\n<br />\n但最仆街既,就係MK車,<br />\n<br />\n住喺新界地區,屋企附近時不時夜晚12點後,<br />\n就聽到D 響喉撚,屌你老母,<br />\n佢地又唔撚係鬥車喎,純粹喺條馬路上,<br />\n大大力踩油<br />\n<br />\n嘈撚到仆街,<br />\n由於喺屋企睇唔撚到部車<br />\n<br />\n咁岩早兩日朝早終於俾我遇到啦!!!<br />\nH車PD7342, 典型MK車既撚樣<br />\n條喉嘈到仆街(但又唔撚係快), 仲要聞撚到D臭味喺條喉出黎<br />\n都唔知係咪入倉油<br />\n<br />\n仲要左攝右攝,CUT線唔打燈<br />\n<br />\n已填左&quot;有缺點車輛舉報表格&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/filemanager/en/content_1178/final%20defective%20vehicle%20report%20form%20(16.08.2016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fen%2Fcontent_1178%2Ffinal%2520defective%2520vehicle%2520report%2520form%2520%2816.08.2016&d=O%2F0Z4sTj8nH98eKxysC4YP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=bbb5f7f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/filemanager/en/content_1178/final%20defective%20vehicle%20report%20form%20(16.08.2016</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n而家見到D響喉撚,都決定見一部投訴一部!!!"},{"pid":"a69ec09a0ba247af200e45b6ce28b4b2e6dc1add","tid":775614,"uid":80308,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"有無人知填呢份FORM同1823,邊樣有效D?"},{"pid":"fb175ac0cd6ac8f3ff442166d3c2d26a06b76c86","tid":775614,"uid":29447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"臭嗰d可能係拆左催化<br />\n放飛劍捉佢去驗廢氣啦"},{"pid":"82c23127824db51fa5d46c5c8dd1dc577ffb28be","tid":775614,"uid":80308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fb175ac0cd6ac8f3ff442166d3c2d26a06b76c86","tid":775614,"uid":29447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T10:19:13.000Z","msg":"臭嗰d可能係拆左催化<br />\n放飛劍捉佢去驗廢氣啦"},"cited